Poor Maps 0.9
=============

 [X] Add framework to list nearby places by type (restaurants, etc.)
 [ ] Add Foursquare provider for listing nearby places
     - Set as default
 [X] Add Nominatim providers for listing nearby places
 [X] Allow tapping on POI markers to show description
